name: the legend of zelda
description:
<font color="1f53d6">this bow measures 12cm in length and 5cm wide.
<font color="3a8be6">it is available with either an alligator clip for a ladies hair bow OR with a shoe clip for a gentleman's bow tie :3
<font color="9d18ea">
please note, that although i spend a lot of time making sure these products are of sturdy quality, please make sure to handle them with care. 
<font color="c560f9">also keep in mind, that due to them being handmade, no two bows will be exactly alike and may look different to the one pictured here :3</font></font></font></font>
